{"tid":1983871,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"慘！加拿大2貨機飛中國載醫療物資 竟兩手空空折返","createTime":"2020-04-22T05:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T04:21:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80386cfebd0d33243e628e0cc74ddbc510fbd8d0","tid":1983871,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"慘！加拿大2貨機飛中國載醫療物資 竟兩手空空折返<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3141504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3141504&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8jQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=fecdf70a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3141504&h=03b6495b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3141504</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎全球爆發之際，疫情趨緩的中國反倒成為主要的醫療物資供應地。計畫從中國運送必要醫療物資回國的加拿大，卻因為碰上物流作業問題，在飛機已抵達中國的情況下竟什麼物品都沒載上，兩手空空原機折返。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大總理杜魯道在疫情例行記者會上談到，一架代表加國政府的班機及一架境內省籍班機，飛往中國載運個人必需物資回國，「很不幸地，貨機必須在沒有載貨的情況下離開，我們正處於與國際競爭個人保護物資（PPE）的局勢當中。」<br />\n<br />\n杜魯道提到，中國正實施非常嚴格的航空管制，限制飛機可在機場停留的時機，即便沒有等到貨品上機，中國政府仍會直接要求離開，「中國機場有許多檢查哨點和隔離措施，供應路線和道路運輸寸步難行。」<br />\n<br />\n但杜魯道強調，過去幾天仍收到數百萬件PPE，預計接下來會有更多的物品運送到加拿大。"},{"pid":"f46023d3c92165a99d667fdbdc7ec5cd11046138","tid":1983871,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"有冇英文原文"},{"pid":"869f71f7930ad4bf75ed5a5c8882ddad098d2312","tid":1983871,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f46023d3c92165a99d667fdbdc7ec5cd11046138","tid":1983871,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"有冇英文原文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"Trudeau: Canadian planes sent to China to pick up medical supplies returned empty<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.com/news/2020/04/21/trudeau-canadian-planes-sent-to-china-to-pick-up-medical-supplies-returned-empty-198794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F04%2F21%2Ftrudeau-canadian-planes-sent-to-china-to-pick-up-medical-supplies-returned-empty-198794&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8jQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=c0892811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.com/news/2020/04/21/trudeau-canadian-planes-sent-to-china-to-pick-up-medical-supplies-returned-empty-198794</a>"},{"pid":"69a7643969ac18487d197961c568949be60b2bf7","tid":1983871,"uid":7369,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:32:38.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦，油價負數，飛咗分分鐘有錢落袋！<br />\n<br />\n杜狗奶夠共未？"},{"pid":"5c093a91db71e213ad3bc71f9b2b8cedd2bbee58","tid":1983871,"uid":89752,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"抵死, 擺明做9你"},{"pid":"c4269d98c644117b90bfc6db71fab1888e1ea090","tid":1983871,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:42:30.000Z","msg":"76Trudeau"},{"pid":"7e88950d0639b2f231acc7b534b27a76672b3055","tid":1983871,"uid":295572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"燒耗啲燃油先，無地方擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597256f9ff4b7da9c073301c8c763d3509c58ca6","tid":1983871,"uid":305261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"加狗比支那撚 奶得咁開心呀啦 <br />\n親手放棄自已煤礦產業 仲投資支那煤礦"},{"pid":"7bc638ad1310e20a349eb33ad15fbbed2f2788a4","tid":1983871,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380649b34ee7ec4713b57158c0365d100b158964","tid":1983871,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-2